1
00:00:11,875 --> 00:00:16,833
♪

2
00:01:35,375 --> 00:01:37,875
[NARRATOR] The Ice Apparition
Yukina, Hiei's sister,

3
00:01:37,958 --> 00:01:40,583
is imprisoned by the
greedy human crime lord,

4
00:01:40,666 --> 00:01:42,333
Gonzou Tarukane.

5
00:01:42,416 --> 00:01:43,875
Yusuke's Spirit Detective team

6
00:01:43,958 --> 00:01:45,958
has entered
Tarukane's stronghold

7
00:01:46,041 --> 00:01:50,375
and defeated three infamous
demons known as the Triad.

8
00:01:50,458 --> 00:01:54,208
Now, only one obstacle stands
in the way of rescuing Yukina

9
00:01:54,291 --> 00:01:56,208
and closing the detective case.

10
00:01:56,291 --> 00:01:59,166
The mysterious Toguro Brothers.

11
00:02:20,708 --> 00:02:23,041
So I guess this
is the big finish!

12
00:02:23,791 --> 00:02:25,625
I can't wait!

13
00:02:25,708 --> 00:02:28,708
Hey! Toguro! Don't blow this!

14
00:02:32,291 --> 00:02:33,666
Poor Tarukane.

15
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:36,458
He's going to have a conniption
before this is finished.

16
00:02:37,166 --> 00:02:38,375
Can't blame him.

17
00:02:38,458 --> 00:02:41,000
It's not often that your
whole financial future

18
00:02:41,083 --> 00:02:42,625
is bet on one match.

19
00:02:42,708 --> 00:02:45,166
Sixty-six trillion dollars!!

20
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:46,750
The loser's got
to sell everything

21
00:02:46,833 --> 00:02:48,708
from their cufflinks
to their organs!

22
00:02:48,791 --> 00:02:50,875
Imagine that on your back!

23
00:02:50,958 --> 00:02:55,041
But Sakyo doesn't
seem to mind! Do you?

24
00:02:56,916 --> 00:02:59,833
[Club men laugh]

25
00:03:02,208 --> 00:03:03,833
Hey, who are those people?

26
00:03:03,916 --> 00:03:06,500
They're watching us risk
our lives like it's funny!

27
00:03:06,583 --> 00:03:08,375
It's awful!

28
00:03:09,375 --> 00:03:11,000
[KUWABARA THINKS]
Have faith, Yukina.

29
00:03:11,083 --> 00:03:13,375
I'm gonna be with you soon!

30
00:03:16,666 --> 00:03:20,625
If we get tired,
please allow us to tap out.

31
00:03:22,708 --> 00:03:24,250
Don't listen Urameshi.

32
00:03:24,333 --> 00:03:27,125
I got a feeling these
guys are up to something!

33
00:03:27,208 --> 00:03:28,791
No joke.

34
00:03:31,250 --> 00:03:34,833
Do you need a backrub,
Koenma sir? You seem tense.

35
00:03:36,625 --> 00:03:39,250
Yusuke can beat them, right?

36
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:43,958
Well, probably not.

37
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:47,833
[KOENMA] But then, I've only
seen them fight once,

38
00:03:47,916 --> 00:03:49,708
and that was many years ago.

39
00:03:52,125 --> 00:03:55,291
But judging from their Spirit
Energy we shouldn't worry.

40
00:03:55,375 --> 00:03:56,541
They're weaklings!

41
00:03:56,625 --> 00:03:58,333
No wait.

42
00:03:58,416 --> 00:04:00,500
I can't really explain it.

43
00:04:00,583 --> 00:04:03,041
But my whole body's
getting this weird vibe.

44
00:04:03,125 --> 00:04:05,916
It's like there's
something big in here.

45
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,666
[KUWABARA] I don't feel nothin.

46
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,333
Ready, brother?

47
00:04:24,916 --> 00:04:26,125
What's that little guy doing?

48
00:04:26,208 --> 00:04:28,708
I bet he's really
popular at parties.

49
00:04:28,791 --> 00:04:32,583
You see my brother is able to
transform the shape of his body.

50
00:04:32,666 --> 00:04:34,750
It's nothing, really.

51
00:04:35,791 --> 00:04:38,458
[KUWBARA] He just
turned into a--a sword!

52
00:04:38,541 --> 00:04:43,291
This is my brother's
specialty. And mine...

53
00:04:52,791 --> 00:04:54,000
Oh, dear!

54
00:04:54,083 --> 00:04:56,625
Further, my Spirit Energy
surrounds my brother

55
00:04:56,708 --> 00:04:59,333
and makes him indestructible.

56
00:04:59,416 --> 00:05:03,000
You see, the Toguro's
truly fight as one.

57
00:05:06,708 --> 00:05:08,875
Whoa, you feel this?

58
00:05:08,958 --> 00:05:13,041
What's up with his power? Dammit
this isn't going to be easy.

59
00:05:13,125 --> 00:05:14,666
Botan step back!

60
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,125
I'll try!

61
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:31,500
They're fast.

62
00:05:33,375 --> 00:05:36,750
Spirit Sword!

63
00:05:40,291 --> 00:05:41,625
Too slow!

64
00:06:07,375 --> 00:06:08,791
No!!!

65
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:17,583
Managed to step back just
enough to avoid a fatal blow.

66
00:06:17,666 --> 00:06:20,833
I'm surprised you had
enough intellect to do that.

67
00:06:24,541 --> 00:06:28,375
But you won't have to scrape
along the floor much longer.

68
00:06:28,458 --> 00:06:32,375
Come now, brother.
Let's send him to Spirit World.

69
00:06:41,458 --> 00:06:44,125
[YUSUKE] Hey forgetting
something, stupid?

70
00:06:44,916 --> 00:06:46,791
Spirit Gun!!

71
00:06:53,833 --> 00:06:56,583
Maybe I didn't
make myself clear!

72
00:06:56,666 --> 00:06:58,666
Shot gun!!!

73
00:07:05,541 --> 00:07:07,083
Son of a bitch!

74
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:20,916
Yes he must think
quite low of us, brother.

75
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,791
As if we can't
deflect a little energy.

76
00:07:23,875 --> 00:07:25,083
[YUSUKE THINKS] Damn it...

77
00:07:25,166 --> 00:07:28,166
Guess there's just
one good way to stop him.

78
00:07:42,458 --> 00:07:44,458
How about point blank?

79
00:07:47,958 --> 00:07:49,750
Spirit Gun!!!

80
00:07:52,708 --> 00:07:53,458
What???

81
00:07:54,291 --> 00:07:55,458
All right!!

82
00:07:55,541 --> 00:07:57,000
Hard to block, huh?

83
00:07:58,125 --> 00:08:01,375
Don't worry, I hear
headless is in this year!

84
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:05,875
What the--?

85
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:10,666
[YUSUKE] I don't believe this!
He turns into a shield, too?

86
00:08:18,958 --> 00:08:20,458
[KUWABARA]
Urameshi!!!

87
00:08:20,541 --> 00:08:22,416
Did I forget to tell you?

88
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:25,583
My brother makes an
excellent defensive weapon.

89
00:08:27,125 --> 00:08:29,625
You're heartless!

90
00:08:29,708 --> 00:08:30,791
Yusuke!

91
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:36,750
[TOGURO 2] I was only
being a professional.

92
00:08:38,375 --> 00:08:40,208
Though I was hoping
you would provide me

93
00:08:40,291 --> 00:08:42,208
much more
entertainment than this!!

94
00:08:48,708 --> 00:08:49,833
They're helpless!

95
00:08:56,958 --> 00:08:58,416
Oh no!!

96
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:02,708
[TARUKANE] Those
Toguro's are invincible!!

97
00:09:02,791 --> 00:09:05,291
I can already smell
my new money comin' in!

98
00:09:05,375 --> 00:09:06,791
[Tarukane laughs]

99
00:09:13,250 --> 00:09:15,791
[TARUKANE] So how you gonna
pay me the trillions, Sakyo?

100
00:09:15,875 --> 00:09:17,666
Cash or credit?

101
00:09:28,333 --> 00:09:30,791
[Toguro 2 laughs]

102
00:09:30,875 --> 00:09:33,541
[KUWABARA THINKS]
I've got to do...

103
00:09:33,625 --> 00:09:35,041
Something!

104
00:09:45,708 --> 00:09:47,041
They're not going to make it!

105
00:09:47,125 --> 00:09:48,458
Are they?

106
00:09:48,958 --> 00:09:52,708
You certain it's them?
The brothers?

107
00:09:52,791 --> 00:09:54,625
I'd never forget that face.

108
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:57,583
[KURAMA] Yusuke is
not ready for them.

109
00:09:57,666 --> 00:10:00,416
[KOENMA] Well of course
he isn't! No one is!

110
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:02,250
Now why hasn't Hiei shown up?

111
00:10:02,333 --> 00:10:04,625
Not that he could put a dent
in the Toguro Brothers either!

112
00:10:04,708 --> 00:10:06,375
Where are you going?

113
00:10:07,041 --> 00:10:10,500
I don't belong here. Voyeurism
has never been my strength.

114
00:10:11,083 --> 00:10:12,208
Excuse me.

115
00:10:14,833 --> 00:10:17,166
I wonder where
he's going, sir.

116
00:10:17,250 --> 00:10:19,625
Over to Tarukane's
stronghold, idiot!

117
00:10:19,708 --> 00:10:23,416
Oh, can he get there
in time to save Yusuke?

118
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:25,708
At this point that
might be impossible.

119
00:10:25,791 --> 00:10:30,375
I just hope he can save
the human crooks from Hiei.

120
00:10:52,666 --> 00:10:55,000
[HIEI] Be strong,
sister. I'm coming.

121
00:11:14,291 --> 00:11:16,625
Let him go!

122
00:11:16,708 --> 00:11:18,125
[TARUKANE]
Feel free to take a little

123
00:11:18,208 --> 00:11:19,708
extra time with them, Toguro!

124
00:11:19,791 --> 00:11:22,375
I know how all you demon
creatures are in to torturing!

125
00:11:22,458 --> 00:11:25,833
Besides, my Black Black Club
could use some good dirty fun!

126
00:11:29,833 --> 00:11:33,583
Why aren't ya lookin', baby?
I know it's the way you like it!

127
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:37,625
Humans getting
killed 'cause of you!

128
00:11:37,708 --> 00:11:39,500
Just like that last one.

129
00:11:47,166 --> 00:11:50,041
[KUWABARA THINKS] Her
memories, I can see them.

130
00:11:51,541 --> 00:11:53,500
My people tell me
these Talisman Cards

131
00:11:53,583 --> 00:11:55,791
can burn the skin right
off an Ice Apparition

132
00:11:55,875 --> 00:11:57,333
with just a
friendly little touch!

133
00:11:57,416 --> 00:11:58,208
Let's try.

134
00:11:58,291 --> 00:11:59,708
Get away!!

135
00:12:00,916 --> 00:12:02,958
Please. Stop!

136
00:12:07,875 --> 00:12:09,666
Put the cards all over her cell!

137
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:12,041
That'll keep her
from goin' anywhere!

138
00:12:15,666 --> 00:12:17,833
[GUARD] I've
brought you some food.

139
00:12:17,916 --> 00:12:20,583
You know you're not going
to be in here forever, Yukina.

140
00:12:23,583 --> 00:12:26,000
You know I've got a
little sister back home

141
00:12:26,083 --> 00:12:27,500
who's about your age now.

142
00:12:28,875 --> 00:12:29,875
[GUARD] Our chance has come!

143
00:12:29,958 --> 00:12:31,791
Tarukane's left
the country on a trip.

144
00:12:31,875 --> 00:12:33,916
Most of the guards are gone!

145
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:38,583
We can't! You'd be in great
danger! What if they caught you!

146
00:12:39,583 --> 00:12:42,708
Come on! Can't you think
about yourself for once?

147
00:12:49,666 --> 00:12:52,666
[TARUKANE] Let's show this
boy what we do to traitors.

148
00:13:07,375 --> 00:13:08,958
[Toguro 2 chuckles]

149
00:13:09,041 --> 00:13:12,291
[TOGURO 2] Tarukane's wrong.
I don't like torture.

150
00:13:12,375 --> 00:13:15,000
At least not when
they're too pathetic

151
00:13:15,083 --> 00:13:16,791
to even defend themselves.

152
00:13:16,875 --> 00:13:18,666
[KUWABARA]
Disgraceful.

153
00:13:24,041 --> 00:13:27,083
And you call yourself a man.

154
00:13:29,250 --> 00:13:31,541
Seeing you live makes me sick.

155
00:13:32,666 --> 00:13:36,625
Interesting, your Spirit
Power has increased greatly.

156
00:13:37,166 --> 00:13:39,208
[Toguro 2 chuckles]

157
00:13:39,291 --> 00:13:42,333
You'll be much more
fun than this carcass.

158
00:13:42,875 --> 00:13:44,250
[BOTAN]
Uh... oh...

159
00:13:44,333 --> 00:13:46,333
Get lost, I'll
have to deal with you

160
00:13:46,416 --> 00:13:48,791
and your brother
some other time.

161
00:13:49,375 --> 00:13:52,291
[KUWABARA] Tarukane's the
one I was talking to.

162
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:56,083
What? You wanna beat me up?

163
00:13:57,833 --> 00:14:02,500
Sorry kid, but I'm
too expensive! Toguro!!

164
00:14:02,583 --> 00:14:06,208
I want this creep
fried extra-crispy!

165
00:14:06,291 --> 00:14:09,500
You heard him.
We don't have a choice.

166
00:14:11,791 --> 00:14:14,708
Get out of my way!!!

167
00:14:33,708 --> 00:14:35,625
Your attacks are very slow.

168
00:14:35,708 --> 00:14:38,333
We can easily predict
your every move.

169
00:14:41,166 --> 00:14:43,500
Kuwabara!

170
00:14:43,583 --> 00:14:47,166
Hey, Urameshi.
I need a favor.

171
00:14:48,375 --> 00:14:51,000
Okay Toguro!
You've had enough fun!

172
00:14:51,083 --> 00:14:53,541
I want to start
collecting my money!

173
00:14:55,666 --> 00:14:57,625
Come on, brother.

174
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:03,000
It's too dangerous! Let's wait!

175
00:15:03,083 --> 00:15:04,625
You know how
fast they move!

176
00:15:04,708 --> 00:15:06,625
This'll only get
you killed quicker!

177
00:15:06,708 --> 00:15:08,375
You haven't seen what I have!

178
00:15:08,458 --> 00:15:10,458
You don't know what
they've done to her!

179
00:15:12,041 --> 00:15:13,000
Please!

180
00:15:14,958 --> 00:15:17,958
Fine, then I've got your back!

181
00:15:18,041 --> 00:15:19,583
Are you ready?

182
00:15:19,666 --> 00:15:20,416
Yeah.

183
00:15:27,708 --> 00:15:29,416
They want to die with honor.

184
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,958
Yes brother.

185
00:15:32,041 --> 00:15:34,250
We will respect their wish!

186
00:15:36,208 --> 00:15:38,333
The battle ends!!

187
00:15:42,375 --> 00:15:44,625
Kuwabara! Here it comes!

188
00:16:02,708 --> 00:16:05,041
[TOGURO 2]
Ingenious plan.

189
00:16:05,125 --> 00:16:08,333
You fighters
are truly something.

190
00:16:13,125 --> 00:16:16,375
What, just happened?

191
00:16:16,458 --> 00:16:19,625
Simple, old friend.
You've lost the bet.

192
00:16:19,708 --> 00:16:22,750
I believe that Sixty-six
trillion, fifty billion...

193
00:16:22,833 --> 00:16:27,375
and two hundred million is
the total you now owe me.

194
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:31,500
Well, I know that you
founded the Black Black Club.

195
00:16:31,583 --> 00:16:36,583
However, I'm afraid we
can't associate with poor men.

196
00:16:37,333 --> 00:16:40,083
Bye! Have fun standing
in the bread lines!

197
00:16:40,166 --> 00:16:42,666
[Club men laugh]

198
00:16:44,625 --> 00:16:46,416
Now Sakashta! Move to plan B!

199
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:49,250
Start the chopper and
make sure Yukina's with us!

200
00:16:49,333 --> 00:16:52,500
Nobody's gonna shut
down Gonzou Tarukane!

201
00:17:08,375 --> 00:17:11,166
The game's over. You ugly fool.

202
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:13,750
I saw the Talisman Cards
hung in the tower.

203
00:17:13,833 --> 00:17:17,541
That explains why I couldn't
find her with my Jagan Eye.

204
00:17:18,250 --> 00:17:21,541
But, you can't run
from death forever.

205
00:17:21,625 --> 00:17:24,666
Wait! I don't know
who the hell you are.

206
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:27,625
But if it's money
you're after. We can talk!

207
00:17:27,708 --> 00:17:28,625
Listen here.

208
00:17:28,708 --> 00:17:30,500
That broad behind
you makes jewels

209
00:17:30,583 --> 00:17:31,625
you wouldn't
even believe!

210
00:17:31,708 --> 00:17:33,541
I could pump
millions from her!

211
00:17:39,666 --> 00:17:41,291
Oh goodness! Hiei!

212
00:17:41,375 --> 00:17:43,833
Hiei's here?!

213
00:17:43,916 --> 00:17:45,458
We have to do something!

214
00:17:45,541 --> 00:17:47,458
Regardless of what
Tarukane deserves,

215
00:17:47,541 --> 00:17:49,958
Hiei is forbidden to
take human life...

216
00:17:50,041 --> 00:17:51,791
He'll be punished severely!

217
00:17:51,875 --> 00:17:53,041
Perfect.

218
00:17:54,916 --> 00:17:58,125
[YUSUKE] Stop it Hiei!
Don't kill him!!

219
00:18:02,083 --> 00:18:04,583
They're just afraid of justice.

220
00:18:10,791 --> 00:18:11,958
[YUKINA] No!!!

221
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:14,041
Please!

222
00:18:14,125 --> 00:18:17,041
No more. I beg of you!

223
00:18:17,125 --> 00:18:18,541
Are you crazy?

224
00:18:18,625 --> 00:18:20,375
Is this not the
man who tormented you

225
00:18:20,458 --> 00:18:22,166
and made you his slave?

226
00:18:22,250 --> 00:18:24,708
He is, I have to bear that.

227
00:18:24,791 --> 00:18:28,083
But taking his life can't wash
away all that he's done to me.

228
00:18:28,166 --> 00:18:30,500
It will only bring more pain.

229
00:18:30,583 --> 00:18:33,166
Just more nightmares.

230
00:18:35,375 --> 00:18:38,958
Please no more!
I can't take it!

231
00:18:45,125 --> 00:18:47,916
Understood,
I won't make you cry.

232
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,333
He's too worthless for that.

233
00:18:50,416 --> 00:18:52,791
How can I ever thank you?

234
00:18:54,583 --> 00:18:56,666
Looks like things
have turned out okay.

235
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,541
Yeah.

236
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:09,541
You seem familiar.

237
00:19:14,125 --> 00:19:17,583
But I'm not sure why.
Who are you?

238
00:19:20,041 --> 00:19:21,708
No one...

239
00:19:23,458 --> 00:19:26,833
[HIEI] Just a member
of the team.

240
00:19:26,916 --> 00:19:29,833
Oh no! I forgot
about them!

241
00:19:32,166 --> 00:19:35,500
[KURAMA] I guess I didn't
need to come here, after all.

242
00:19:35,583 --> 00:19:38,000
How long have you
been standing there.

243
00:19:38,083 --> 00:19:39,708
Long enough, right?

244
00:19:39,791 --> 00:19:42,083
Why don't you want
to tell the girl?

245
00:19:42,166 --> 00:19:44,833
She deserves to
know she has a brother.

246
00:19:44,916 --> 00:19:47,750
She deserves to be happy.

247
00:19:47,833 --> 00:19:50,958
[KURAMA] I thought
the two were the same.

248
00:19:51,041 --> 00:19:53,000
This is the way I want it.

249
00:19:54,625 --> 00:19:55,791
Everybody's okay.

250
00:19:55,875 --> 00:19:58,541
But, why don't you
go see him to make sure.

251
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:07,250
Yukina!

252
00:20:07,333 --> 00:20:11,000
Stay still, I can use some of
my power to heal your wounds.

253
00:20:17,208 --> 00:20:19,541
Hey, let's go see
what's happening upstairs.

254
00:20:21,583 --> 00:20:25,000
Oh yes, of course!
Good old upstairs!

255
00:20:25,458 --> 00:20:28,458
I'm sorry, you were
hurt because of me.

256
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:32,166
[KUWABARA]
Your burn.

257
00:20:32,833 --> 00:20:36,750
You got that from
Tarukane, I saw it.

258
00:20:38,125 --> 00:20:40,375
I'm the one who
should be saying sorry.

259
00:20:40,458 --> 00:20:43,166
For not saving you earlier.

260
00:20:44,333 --> 00:20:47,125
[KUWABARA] You probably
hate humans, don't you?

261
00:20:49,166 --> 00:20:51,666
[YUSUKE] Wow! We've
got a full house, huh?

262
00:20:53,166 --> 00:20:55,000
[KUWABARA]
I can't blame you for it.

263
00:20:55,083 --> 00:20:57,250
There's lots of
stupid humans out there.

264
00:20:57,333 --> 00:21:00,208
Heck, most the guys I know.

265
00:21:01,291 --> 00:21:04,083
But there's, there's
some good ones, too.

266
00:21:04,166 --> 00:21:08,875
Don't hate us! I can
show you the good side!

267
00:21:13,583 --> 00:21:15,791
Don't worry.

268
00:21:15,875 --> 00:21:18,833
Really, I like humans.

269
00:21:22,458 --> 00:21:24,208
Very much.

270
00:21:41,208 --> 00:21:43,166
Thank you.

271
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:55,750
[YUSUKE] Well that wraps
my casework work for now,

272
00:21:55,833 --> 00:21:57,541
but I hope everyone's
ready the next one,

273
00:21:57,625 --> 00:22:00,208
because you haven't
seen anything yet!

274
00:22:00,291 --> 00:22:02,208
A giant new adventure
is about to begin,

275
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:04,250
filled with a couple
villains you know already,

276
00:22:04,333 --> 00:22:06,583
and about thirty
more that you don't!

277
00:22:07,291 --> 00:22:10,041
I'll have to take a trip
to my favorite psychic fossil,

278
00:22:10,125 --> 00:22:12,500
after a special visitor
shows up on my home turf

279
00:22:12,583 --> 00:22:14,208
with a very deadly threat!

280
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:15,791
It'll be training, fighting,

281
00:22:15,875 --> 00:22:20,750
and plenty of my killer jokes,
when Yu Yu Hakusho continues!

282
00:22:22,625 --> 00:22:27,583
♪

